{"tid":990694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信德中心男子吊頸跳落水　當場不治","createTime":"2019-01-21T20:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T21:07:58.000Z","uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"66895b3ed73345586a16ca04cb85be5d19f36975","tid":990694,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T20:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190121/large/1548033582_722f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190121%2Flarge%2F1548033582_722f.jpg&h=5d28b8b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子在碼頭邊吊頸，半身浸在水中。(劉永明攝)<br />\n<br />\n上環信德中心，今晨8時50分，一名男子被發現頸纏電線，吊在碼頭外。他滿頭白髮，穿著深色外套，下半身浸在水中，面向牆。消防員到場將他拉起，經救護員檢驗證實不治。警方初步相信他頸纏電線後，跨出欄杆跳落水，警方經調查後獲悉事主姓黎（68歲），於現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=LP25UddgDlQPT8s18mXU6cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6e8054c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190121/59165785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59165785&d=LP25UddgDlQPT8s18mXU6cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ee41bb6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59165785&h=998673cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190121/59165785</a>"},{"pid":"2b712e30acc817d81e39ba1b961cb45661ba2d42","tid":990694,"uid":42379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"嘩 真係咁恐怖嘅自己方式都畀佢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}